{"id":208124,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/江泽民：“你来当总书记”/","date":"2012-02-03T02:21:07Z","modified":"2012-02-03T02:24:18Z","title":"总书记是如何产生的：“你来当总书记”","content":"<p>来源：<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzE4NTIzNDQ0.html\">优酷网</a></p>\n<p>在央视对江泽民视察中国联合工程公司的专题报道中，江泽民发表了如下讲话：</p>\n<p>“我绝对不知道，我作为一个上海市委书记怎么把我选到北京去了。 所以邓小平同志同我讲话，说‘中央都决定了，你来党总书记。’ 我说另请高明吧，我实在也不是谦虚，我一个上海市委书记怎么到北京来了呢？但是， 小平同志讲‘大家已经研究决定了。’ 所以后来我念了两首诗，叫‘苟利国家生死以，岂因福祸避趋之。’ 所以我就到了北京。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/%e6%b1%9f%e6%b3%bd%e6%b0%91%ef%bc%9a%e2%80%9c%e4%bd%a0%e6%9d%a5%e5%bd%93%e6%80%bb%e4%b9%a6%e8%ae%b0%e2%80%9d/jiang01/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-208125\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208125\" title=\"jiang01\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/jiang01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/jiang01.png 608w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/jiang01-300x212.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/%e6%b1%9f%e6%b3%bd%e6%b0%91%ef%bc%9a%e2%80%9c%e4%bd%a0%e6%9d%a5%e5%bd%93%e6%80%bb%e4%b9%a6%e8%ae%b0%e2%80%9d/jiang02/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-208126\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208126\" title=\"jiang02\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/jiang02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"605\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/jiang02.png 605w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/jiang02-300x217.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 605px) 100vw, 605px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以下为完整讲话：<br />\n<object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMzE4NTIzNDQ0/v.swf\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMzE4NTIzNDQ0/v.swf\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" quality=\"high\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" /></object></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[20534],"tags":[18834,18553,11531]}